source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_SEQ_00<tab>Abaka looks at you with an incredulous glint in his eye.
target: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_SEQ_00<tab>明けの玉座のアバカは、旅人のことを試したいようだ。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_000<tab>Oi, you! Hold it right there. You are the <var 08 E905 ((woman)) ((man)) /var> rumored to have conquered Bardam's Mettle, are you not?
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_000<tab>ちょっと待て。
貴様、バルダム覇道を越えたと聞いたが、本当か？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_001<tab>I strain to believe that <var 1A 02 /var>you<var 1A 01 /var>, an outsider, would be able to pass the very trial even trained warriors of the Steppe struggle to overcome. If you are as great as they say, you should have no trouble passing my little test.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_001<tab>外から来た貴様が、あの試練を突破するとは到底思えん。
……だが、俺が与える試練をも越えるならば、信じてやろう。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_002<tab>To the northwest are khun chuluu. Defeat four and perhaps the rumors hold a grain of the truth. Should you fail to do so, however, I shall know you are naught more than a charlatan.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_002<tab>ここより北西の、キオルエンに生息する、
「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2169201 /var>」を4体倒してこい。
達成できなくば、覇道の件は、ただの噂に過ぎなかったと見なす。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_003<tab>Slaying four khun chuluu is but child's play for a son of Azim. If you're half as strong as I have been led to believe you should have no problem.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_003<tab>もし貴様が、太陽神アジムの子たるオロニル族にも、
ひけをとらぬ戦士ならば、これくらい簡単であろう？

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_004<tab>Ha! Come back already with your tail between your legs, have you? I knew you were not the warrior you were cracked up to be.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_004<tab>ここより北西の、キオルエンに生息する、
「<var 28 ((BNpcName)) F2169201 /var>」を4体倒してこい。
達成できなくば、覇道の件は、ただの噂に過ぎなかったと見なす。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_010<tab>That you would rise to the challenge and face four of the deadly monsters regardless of the fact that no one would be there to congratulate you on your triumph─you are a warrior in the truest sense of the word.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_010<tab>誰も見ていないにも関わらず、
己が強さを証明するためだけに戦うとは、貴様は誠の戦士だな。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_011<tab>How do I know, you ask? I watched you from the skies, atop my yol.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_011<tab>だが安心せよ、俺は見ていたぞ。
ヨルの背に乗り、遙か上空からな。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_012<tab>...It seems I owe you an apology. I should not have doubted your abilities.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_012<tab>確かに貴様には、あの覇道を越えるだけの資質があるようだ。
……疑ってすまなかったな。

source: TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_013<tab>In proving your strength you have won my respect. I shall be sure to regale the others with tales of your fighting prowess.
target:
TEXT_STMBDZ523_02774_ABAKA_000_013<tab>オロニル族は、強き者には相応の敬意を示す。
俺の与えた試練に打ち勝った腕を、称えてやろう。
